# 1. Ignore EVERYTHING in the repository (skips your 16GB of data)
**

# 2. Allow specific project and source folders needed for the build
!test/OpenCvSharp.Cuda.Console.Test/**
!src/OpenCvSharp.Cuda/**
!src/build/linux/Combined/**

# 3. Allow standard solution-level config files (if you use them)
!*.sln
!NuGet.Config
!Directory.Build.props
!Directory.Build.targets
!global.json

# 4. RE-IGNORE the bin and obj folders so you don't copy local Windows build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.vs/